Jean-François Stévenin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean-Fran%C3%A7ois_St%C3%A9venin 0 Jean-François Stévenin (French: [stevnɛ̃]; born 23 April 1944) is a French actor and filmmaker. He has appeared in 150 films and television shows since 1968. He starred in the film Cold Moon, which was entered into the 1991 Cannes Film Festival.
